languages.text: [draft]The Psyker and their allies gain a +<u>5×(Psyker's {g|Encyclopedia:PsyRating}psy rating{/g})</u>% {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} to {g|Encyclopedia:OverpenetrationFullGlossary}overpenetration{/g} chance for ranged attacks, and their attacks have a −15% less chance to be parried.

traits.locale_text: [draft]The Psyker and their allies gain a +<u>5×(Psyker's psy rating)</u>% bonus to overpenetration chance for ranged attacks, and their attacks have a −15% less chance to be parried.
